## 6. âœ… Expected Outcomes
- Show that the **Cosmic Tension Equation** can reproduce epidemic waves with fewer assumptions than SEIR.  
- Demonstrate robustness across **different diseases (flu vs COVID-19)** and **different geographies**.  
